<div class="center">
<figure class="image-placeholder"><img alt="20210402_tw_tai_lu_ge_chu_gui_3_Large.jpg" src="https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20210402/20210402_tw_tai_lu_ge_chu_gui_3_Large.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption>现场疑似变形的列车部件。（互联网）</figcaption></figure>
</div>

<p>花莲县消防局已出动12车35人赶往现场进行救援，新北市也支援10台救护车。</p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1-wrapper" class="dfp-tag-wrapper">
<div id="dfp-ad-imu1" class="dfp-tag-wrapper">
      
</div>
</div></section>

<p>根据通报，出事列车共八节车厢，搭车乘客约350人，第一至三车厢已疏散约60人，四至五节车厢变形抢救中，初步目视多人无生命征象。</p>

